#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.236"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.236:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.236:0.2"
msgid "24. Āvāsikavagga "
msgstr "24. A Resident Mendicant "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.236:0.3"
msgid "236. Paṭhamaavaṇṇārahasutta "
msgstr "236. Deserving Criticism (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.236:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a resident mendicant with five qualities is cast down to hell. "

msgctxt "an5.236:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.236:1.3"
msgid "Ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā avaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati; "
msgstr "Without examining or scrutinizing, they praise those deserving of criticism, "

msgctxt "an5.236:1.4"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā vaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati; "
msgstr "and they criticize those deserving of praise. "

msgctxt "an5.236:1.5"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā appasādanīye ṭhāne pasādaṃ upadaṃseti; "
msgstr "Without examining or scrutinizing, they arouse faith in things that are dubious, "

msgctxt "an5.236:1.6"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā pasādanīye ṭhāne appasādaṃ upadaṃseti; "
msgstr "and they don’t arouse faith in things that are inspiring. "

msgctxt "an5.236:1.7"
msgid "saddhādeyyaṃ vinipāteti. "
msgstr "And they waste a gift given in faith. "

msgctxt "an5.236:1.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "A resident mendicant with these five qualities is cast down to hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.236:2.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge. "
msgstr "A resident mendicant with five qualities is raised up to heaven. "

msgctxt "an5.236:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.236:2.3"
msgid "Anuvicca pariyogāhetvā avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati; "
msgstr "After examining and scrutinizing, they criticize those deserving of criticism, "

msgctxt "an5.236:2.4"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati; "
msgstr "and they praise those deserving of praise. "

msgctxt "an5.236:2.5"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā appasādanīye ṭhāne appasādaṃ upadaṃseti; "
msgstr "They don’t arouse faith in things that are dubious, "

msgctxt "an5.236:2.6"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā pasādanīye ṭhāne pasādaṃ upadaṃseti; "
msgstr "and they do arouse faith in things that are inspiring. "

msgctxt "an5.236:2.7"
msgid "saddhādeyyaṃ na vinipāteti. "
msgstr "And they don’t waste a gift given in faith. "

msgctxt "an5.236:2.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge”ti. "
msgstr "A resident mendicant with these five qualities is raised up to heaven.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.236:2.9"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

